data.title: NATS Test Materials
data.meta_description: NATS Test Materials - Free download as Word Doc (.doc), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. NATS provides Air Traffic control service at two en-route centres, Swanwick (including London Area control centre and London terminal control Centre) and Prestwick (including the Oceanic Control function) the centre handles in excess of 3 million movements a year. Successful recruits will join the team of professionals who work for NATS at the various units around the country.
